snippet.title: PlayStation - Tennis no Oji-Sama - Sweat & Tears (2002) - Opening
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Tennis no Oji-Sama: Sweat & Tears is a Sports game, developed by Tenky and published by Konami, which was released in Japan in 2002.
